{"type": "article", "id": 48671, "title": "优衣库要在非洲建厂，以及，Nike 发布最新 NBA 城市球衣 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-12-28T03:41:36Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 2106, "name": "NBA"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171228111338uMWw0dBnl7945KCm.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.cpp-luxury.com/marriott-international-to-open-40-luxury-hotels-in-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>万豪国际计划明年新开 40 家酒店</strong></a> | 旗下拥有 The Ritz-Carlton、Ritz-Carlton Reserve、St. Regis、W Hotels、The Luxury Collection、EDITION 和 JW Marriott 等品牌的万豪（Marriott）国际酒店集团宣布，2018 年将在全球新开 40 家酒店，进驻 25 个新兴国家，包括古巴、菲律宾、尼泊尔、冰岛等。另外，万豪的开店计划中有 6 家新店都在中国。</p><p><a href=\"http://footwearnews.com/2017/business/retail/holiday-shopping-sales-retail-consumer-confidence-472400/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>因为折扣力度大，今年假日季零售看起来要比去年好</strong></a> | 根据美国国家零售业联盟的数据，今年 11、12 月的零售业销售额比去年增长了 3.6% 至 4％，最终数字可能达到 6820 亿美元。该机构的媒体关系主管 Ana Smith 指出，过去几个月里，失业率较低，工资有所上升，消费者的信心指数更高，另外，零售业的折扣力度更大也是吸引消费的重要原因。</p><p><a href=\"https://zh.cn.nikkei.com/industry/management-strategy/28541-2017-12-27-08-55-30.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>优衣库要在非洲建厂，埃塞俄比亚或将成为欧美市场的主要出口基地</strong></a> | 优衣库计划，最早将在 2018 年于非洲国家埃塞俄比亚启动衬衫等服装的试生产，如果产品质量和品质能够达标，将逐渐增加产能，埃塞俄比亚有望成为针对欧美市场的服装出口基地。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/converse-all-star-chuck-70-hi-varsity-jacket/#slide-4\" rel=\"nofollow\">Converse Chuck Taylor All Star </a>发布了一款灵感来自棒球外套的球鞋，这双鞋由皮革打造，特点是鞋侧的一个绒线“C”。它售价 100 美元，现已登陆 Converse 门店。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110440hAMIyFQLq19eWZSG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201712281104387kbypJ3RLSfqYzX9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110438OdxYZvlA2Mf5yN9s.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110438iOMsLcTWqjY7oIBR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://stylfile.com/products/stylpro\" rel=\"nofollow\">StylePro </a>是一款化妆刷的清洗甩干工具，它可以配备多款不同大小的刷头，只需要把刷子放进机器里，配上清洁剂，10 秒就可以清洗干净并甩干。这款设备的发明者是美国电视节目 The Apprentice 的获奖者，它号称可以改变美妆界，售价 63 美元。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110459WINBgPp8h31ZRynT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666034\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110459wbWtQCDM9Nyz3Vga.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666034\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110459t52vUXImDdA8gzex.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666034\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110459Lyc6IVrzmSJKsRTv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.700000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110459C6peoLuxmUMVBlGP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667932\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110459TvRbx5eGJmXOyrNc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201712281105154omxJqZtWyVhsG3g.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.freshnessmag.com/2017/12/27/nike-nba-city-edition-uniforms/#gid=ci021d6a2d100025f0&amp;pid=nike-nba-city-edition-uniform-06\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nike 发布了新一季的城市系列 NBA 球衣。</a>在 Nike 正式签约 NBA 之后，改变了球衣发布的规则，球衣不再分主客场，而是改为了联盟、州、城市发布，共有四款不同的设计。这款是为了庆祝联盟里 30 支球队建立而发布的。 </p><p>来看一下本赛季的城市球衣，除了休斯敦火箭队、迈阿密热火队、纽约尼克斯队和多伦多猛龙队，他们将在晚些时候公布他们的队服。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110615NXVJ57GKlS8yxIBW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110616vAi5Q74n2RmGUHBg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110628MisanL9q0ykRmKZC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201712281105544Vdxyw1GAiglctRE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110554wjVaCl6RgHPYAyJt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110554TcNUEbukXISoAVdv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110555ty9Hf263uka01CcL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110555Ah0fPjli5avSeNbH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110555UWYKFH9Tv5erwE0q.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110555LbUIexmwWjafMGJh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110555GkwLzq2eDnOau5dY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110555GDd8VlComw19FBTM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110555H3FxCPlcJnjN5IQm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110555XvYGJz8lSNQZtCcE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110555KogbHAarkn6DFyB5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110555WriLvwC81cEKBnVQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110555JPXnqGowi5RmNfjE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110555KgOdqafuz7mrYyEi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110556fy64xiYseIUuRpSj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110556o8IjAx9WTV4b0f2B.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110556j60nYrvmes8kPKc9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201712281105562aF0mlQCLIo1EBnz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110556V2uiBf3RGESTM5eJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110556FBJWrXisnOCVfm7g.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110556KbAQiRna5Y2UGNM1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201712281105566Eex8ALkdHC1RSgQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110556zpfGCWhZc1UD58Tw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201712281105563KOmoxUe1XwYy9hi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110556iyNaCMnBXZGQ4m0q.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>2017 年的性侵风波不断，一个来自布鲁克林的组织 America Hates Me 发布了一款名为<a href=\"http://wwd.com/eye/lifestyle/america-hates-us-believe-women-shirts-to-help-victims-share-their-stories-of-abuse-11082405/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Believe Woman </a>的 T 恤来声讨这种行为。 </p><p><a href=\"http://americahates.us/\" rel=\"nofollow\">America Hates Me </a>这种组织还挺酷的，他们所得收入的 20% 都将捐给公益机构，赫芬顿邮报称他们是“盛开在纽约混凝土缝隙中的小小花朵”。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110655LHz5BMJZjUvhqCKf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.648438\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110655HqCd64aInSjtVxPg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.999000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>Nike 将于一月份上架的 <a href=\"https://sneakernews.com/tag/nike-air-more-money/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Air More Money </a>系列有意思，这个系列目前共发布了四款不同的货币版本，有美元、欧元（法国）、英镑和日元。<br></p><p>这四款鞋子的配色各不相同，鞋面刺绣文字、后跟处的国旗 logo 和货币符号，包括鞋底的设计都藏着不少小心思。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110740CWcwsAMGvZ8fUYpO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.701754\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110732OMWxIASfpubZ0wKV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.702632\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110740dcrWqLKFNXH7RCsM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.702632\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110732ZvxhstirXaOzyJ7w.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.702632\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110732grIKFyNJPAqBCGlx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110730HRPnzwudMeBSr26y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.702632\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110734xTPFngDQk3JjrRaN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.702632\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201712281107397XAz9vmHn8dpNRqw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.702632\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110738HSquZ3pIadJ4gTPE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110737mkBpoJ2TPQrLuFC7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.702632\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110728plqRbamJBIXgTkEn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.702632\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110737YfZsW4T3kFV7NLpU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.702632\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201712281107370dKTJGnm6bXgNF75.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228110726LGeXxZzlrsYRyOgT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.702632\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228111054uJOSPhyAeI4XTQFM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.668182\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228111054BRG8pY6lQqVSbDmg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.668182\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201712281109451vxbjGgD7ZMRPyqo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.701754\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：Converse</p>"}